{
  "page": "Maegi",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>A <i><b>maegi</b></i> is a woman of <a href=\"/index.php/Essos\" title=\"Essos\">Essos</a> who practices <a href=\"/index.php/Bloodmagic\" title=\"Bloodmagic\">bloodmagic</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> According to <a href=\"/index.php/Mirri_Maz_Duur\" title=\"Mirri Maz Duur\">Mirri Maz Duur</a>, the word means \"wise\".<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> \n</p><p>The bloodmagic of <i>maegi</i> is hated, mistrusted, and forbidden by the <a href=\"/index.php/Dothraki\" title=\"Dothraki\">Dothraki</a>, who claim that the <i>maegi</i> lie with <a href=\"/index.php/Demons\" title=\"Demons\">demons</a> and come to men in the dark of night to suck life and strength from their bodies. They may sometimes go so far as to kill anyone even assumed to be a <i>maegi</i>, to prevent her from cursing them with evil magic.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup> <i>Maegi</i> often show a remarkable capability of telling one's future, usually from a drop of blood.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The Dothraki also use the word to refer to other types of magic practitioners, such as the <a href=\"/index.php/Warlocks\" title=\"Warlocks\">warlocks</a> of <a href=\"/index.php/Qarth\" title=\"Qarth\">Qarth</a> and the <a href=\"/index.php/Undying_Ones\" title=\"Undying Ones\">Undying Ones</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_5-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok48.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup><sup id=\"cite_ref-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_6-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Racok63.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Known_or_reputed_maegi\">Known or reputed <i>maegi</i></span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maegi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Known or reputed maegi\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/index.php/Mirri_Maz_Duur\" title=\"Mirri Maz Duur\">Mirri Maz Duur</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Godswife\" title=\"Godswife\">godswife</a> of the <a href=\"/index.php/Great_Shepherd\" title=\"Great Shepherd\">Great Shepherd</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Maggy\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Maggy\">Maggy the Frog</a>, a fortune teller once established in <a href=\"/index.php/Lannisport\" title=\"Lannisport\">Lannisport</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/index.php/Yna\" title=\"Yna\">Yna</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Prostitute\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Prostitute\">prostitute</a> at the <a href=\"/index.php/Happy_Port\" title=\"Happy Port\">Happy Port</a> in <a href=\"/index.php/Braavos\" title=\"Braavos\">Braavos</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Maegi&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: References\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">↑ <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">1.0</a></sup> <sup><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot61.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-1\">1.1</a></sup></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_61\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 61\">Chapter 61</a>, Daenerys VII.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos19.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_19\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 19\">Chapter 19</a>, Tyrion III.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Ragot72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Ragot72.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones\" title=\"A Game of Thrones\">A Game of Thrones</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Game_of_Thrones-Chapter_72\" title=\"A Game of Thrones-Chapter 72\">Chapter 72</a>, Daenerys X.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Raffc34.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_4-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows\" title=\"A Feast for Crows\">A Feast for Crows</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Feast_for_Crows-